Package ca.ualberta.cs.corgFu

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IView
    Interface that allows for an MVC design.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllQuestionsApplication
    The singleton class that allows for a singular allQuestions model to be accessed and updated by a singular controller.
    choiceSingleton
    This is a singleton that allows for the calling of the choice outide of the class for data management.
    ConnectedManager
    This is the class that is called by all activities to determine whether or not the application has connection.
    DataManager
    This is a class that handles all of our data, saving each respective type of data in a particular save directory.
    InsertAnswerAdapter
    The custom ArrayAdapter that allows a custom view to be inserted in an android ListView.
    InsertQuestionAdapter
    The custom ArrayAdapter that allows a custom view to be inserted in an android ListView.
    InsertReplyAdapter
    The custom ArrayAdapter that allows a custom view to be inserted in an android ListView.
    Model<V extends IView>
    A class that allows for MVC design and allows for the implementation of the model portion of MVC.
    OfflineDataAdapter  
    Picture
    This is an abstract class that performs all the needed methods required for handling pictures which includes determining whether or not the image meets the size requirements and finally associating the image to either the Answer/Question objects.
    UserName
    The username class is a singleton that holds all relevant information that the application may need to access.
